name: Filling void, Inverted bust, 2021
description:
collage, coffee, acrylic on paper, cm 20x30
part of the series Filling Void, a collection of mixed media works started mid 2020 trying to investigate the opposite concepts of full and void with painting, collage and digital print, in this case a cutout silhouette of a bust out an old revue revealed in his back an intriguing figures composition.
